history.content:
Edvisee if an edutech startup that provides blockchain academic credential to students. We aim to streamline school application process and give back full ownership of academic credentials to student.

We’re #hiring. Know anyone who might be interested?
#blockchaintechnology #ucberkeley #softwaredevelopment #softwareengineer

If you are interested. Please email mksiregar@berkeley.edu with your resume!
